## IronLedger VM Configuration
## Node name and cookie for distributed Erlang
-name ironledger@127.0.0.1
-setcookie ironledger_secret_cookie

## Enable kernel polling for better I/O performance
+K true

## Enable heartbeat monitoring for permanent applications
-heart

## Process limit
+P 1000000

## Port range for distributed Erlang
-kernel inet_dist_listen_min 9100 inet_dist_listen_max 9150
